  m_text: 'Pattern B: TWO non-overlapping clips [1,3.5] and [6,8.5] on a 10s loop. Each window detaches fresh (re-captures parent+pose) and reattaches at its own end. Between the windows the child is parented and rides the orbiting parent. NO Blending cap -> clips must never overlap.'
