  m_text: 'Pattern C: one clip with ClipCaps.Looping pulsing detach on a short 3s loop. Each loop re-runs the ENTER capture and EXIT restore -> the child repeatedly pops loose and snaps back. Every loop pays one end-of-frame ECB structural change (use sparingly).'
